# {{project_name}}

A minimal Tessera UI starter that renders a full-screen surface with a
`Hello World` label so you can focus on wiring real components.

## Features

- Preconfigured Tessera renderer with basic component pipelines
- `src/lib.rs` entrypoint generated via `tessera_ui::entry!` with pipeline registration
- Ready-to-edit `Cargo.toml` for Tessera apps

## Running

```bash
cargo tessera dev
```

## Building

```bash
cargo tessera build --release
```

